OL,3,CDifferent IT systems in Wales and
OL,4,CEngland posing 'unacceptable patient
OL,5,Crisk'
OL,7,FThe failure of IT systems to
OL,8,Fcommunicate between the NHS here and
OL,9,Fin England is posing "an unacceptable
OL,10,Fclinical risk," Welsh MPs have been
OL,11,Ftold.
OL,13,FMembers of the Welsh Affairs Select
OL,14,FCommittee have been questioning
OL,15,Fdoctors' and patients' representatives
OL,16,Fas well as health chiefs from both
OL,17,Fsides of the border.
