OL,3,CDifferent IT systems in Wales and
OL,4,CEngland posing 'unacceptable patient
OL,5,Crisk'
OL,7,FThey were told that around 37,00 Welsh
OL,8,Fpatients are seen in the English NHS
OL,9,Feach year but the meeting also
OL,10,Fhighlighted a lack of communication.
OL,12,FLiberal Democrat MP David Chadwick
OL,13,Fsaid that a previous report by the
OL,14,Fcommittee in 2015 "noted that having
OL,15,Fdifferent IT systems in Wales and
OL,16,FEngland has a real impact on patient
OL,17,Fcare, and in your written submission
OL,18,Fthat you tell us that there remain
OL,19,Fproblems today, that's something that
OL,20,FI see a lot of in my inbox.
OL,26,@vD@SOU
