OL,4,CEngland posing 'unacceptable patient
OL,5,Crisk'
OL,7,F"Just this week, I had a constituent
OL,8,Fcontact me to tell me about her late
OL,9,Fhusband's experience of receiving
OL,10,Fcancer treatment at Hereford Hospital.
OL,11,FHe was receiving treatment there, and
OL,12,Fthen he needed urgent, emergency end
OL,13,Fof life care, and was admitted to
OL,14,FNeville Hall Hospital in Abergavenny,
OL,15,Fbut the team in Neville Hall were
OL,16,Funable to access his English hospital
OL,17,Fnotes.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
