OL,3,CDifferent IT systems in Wales and
OL,4,CEngland posing 'unacceptable patient
OL,5,Crisk'
OL,7,F"So what's been the main barrier to
OL,8,Fdeveloping a joined-up IT system,
OL,9,Fgiven this committee recommended it 10
OL,10,Fyears ago, what do you believe could
OL,11,Fbe done to solve it? Does it simply
OL,12,Fcome down to a lack of political will?"
OL,14,FDr David Bailey, the former chair of
OL,15,Fthe British Medical Association's
OL,16,FWelsh council said that there's no
OL,17,Freason why the two IT systems
OL,18,Fshouldn't be able to communicate with
OL,19,Feach other.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@gO]
