OL,3,CDifferent IT systems in Wales and
OL,4,CEngland posing 'unacceptable patient
OL,5,Crisk'
OL,7,F"At the moment, GPs can communicate
OL,8,Fwith hospitals perfectly
OL,9,Felectronically in Wales. They can do
OL,10,Fexactly the same in England. But if
OL,11,Fone of you is in Bristol and one of
OL,12,Fyou is in Cardiff, it's hopeless, and
OL,13,Fthat's because they just don't talk to
OL,14,Feach other."
OL,16,FHe told the MPs that "it does need
OL,17,Fgovernment action, I think probably it
OL,18,Fneeds Welsh action for this."
