OL,7,FSenior managers from the NHS on both
OL,8,Fsides of the border have also been
OL,9,Fgiving evidence to the committee. They
OL,10,Ftold the MPs that there is long-
OL,11,Fstanding cross-border cooperation.
OL,13,FThey were asked about the suggestion
OL,14,Fthat patients from Wales should be
OL,15,Foffered treatment in England to speed
OL,16,Fup waiting lists.
