OL,7,FCarol Shillabeer who's the Chief
OL,8,FExecutive of Betsi Cadwaladr
OL,9,FUniversity Health Board said patients
OL,10,Fare already being offered that option
OL,11,Fand are willing to travel, but there
OL,12,Fmay not be the spare capacity in the
OL,13,FEnglish NHS to treat them.
