OL,7,FShe told MPs that "most patients would
OL,8,Flike to have as much care close to
OL,9,Fhome as they can. But some will
OL,10,Fcertainly travel, and we have been
OL,11,Flooking to offer those opportunities
OL,12,Fto people here in North Wales, both
OL,13,FNHS, but also non-NHS, provider
OL,14,Fopportunities."
