OL,7,FBut she added "that is not always
OL,8,Fstraightforward, because obviously,
OL,9,Fcolleagues are trying to meet the
OL,10,Fneeds of patients in their own area,
OL,11,Fbut we do have a collaboration where
OL,12,Fan organization can help, I have found
OL,13,Fthat they usually do...
OL,15,F"So there's no problem with the will,
OL,16,Fthere's probably more of a challenge
OL,17,Faround capacity, and that's a more
OL,18,Fdifficult point to fully address."
